<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Vista Heights</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established back in 1962, the community in <span class="par-xl">Vista Heights is highly reputed for its mid century charm combined with top notch modern conveniences suited to the contemporary lifestyle</span>. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community borders the South Airways Industrial Area on the north and east and is bounded by the Deerfoot Trail and the Trans-Canada Highway on the western and southern edge respectively.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">A majority of the homes for sale in Vista Heights comprise a mix of luxurious bungalows and townhouses that are typically listed at an average price of $360,000. </p>
        </div>
